  "Description": {
    "English": "An <span class=\"name name-catalyst\">advanced catalyst</span>, useful for charging <span class=\"name name-commodity\">defensive technologies</span> such as shields or hazard protection.<br> <br>Created in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span>, or occasionally found in crystalline form on a planet's surface.<br><br>Offers a substantially improved energy-per-gram ratio over regular Sodium.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">高级催化剂</span>，用于为<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防御技术</span>（如护盾和危险防护）充能。<br> <br>通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>制造，偶尔也可在行星表面发现其晶体形式。<br><br>提供了比常规钠显著改进的每克能量比。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">高级催化剂</span>，用于为<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防御技术</span>（如护盾和危险防护）充能。<br> <br>通过<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>制造，偶尔也可在行星表面发现其晶体形式。<br><br>提供了比常规钠显著改进的每克能量比。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">先進催化劑</span>，能用來為防護罩或風險防護系統等<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防衛科技</span>充能。<br> <br>由<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>製成，有時也會在星球地表以結晶形態出現。<br><br>比起一般鈉，每單位重量可提供的能量大幅提升。"
  },
