  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">Sodium Nitrate</span> is created from Sodium in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span><br>Sodium Nitrate is also found in crystal form. Locate sodium nitrate crystals with the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Scanner</span> (<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>). Mining requires use of an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Advanced Mining Laser</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">硝酸钠</span>可采用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>从钠中制得<br>硝酸钠也是晶体形式的。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描仪</span>（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）定位硝酸钠晶体。开采需要使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级开采光束</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">硝酸钠</span>可采用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>从钠中制得<br>硝酸钠也是晶体形式的。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描仪</span>（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）定位硝酸钠晶体。开采需要使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级开采光束</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">硝酸鈉</span>是透過使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>從鈉製造出來的。<br>硝酸鈉也以結晶形式出現。用<span class=\"name name-technology\">掃描器</span>（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）找出硝酸鈉結晶。開採時需要用到<span class=\"name name-technology\">改良採礦雷射</span>。"
  },
  "PinObjectiveMessage": {
