    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描仪</span>（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）定位<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">硝酸钠</span><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>中加工钠以制作硝酸钠",
